snippet.textDisplay:
Beautiful singing by Maestros.

This song is in Raaga Aiman(Yaman), Best thing about Raaga Aiman is that it's Notes needs not to be embellished(Rachaana), They are already in a beautiful pattern of ascending and descending.

Arrangement and instruments used in the song are not complimenting the singing as much as they should.

I would have considered this as a Good effort as far as the arrangement and instrumentation is concerned if this was Coke Studio Season 1, After 6 out Class seasons this effort sounds mediocre. Should have been a master piece.
snippet.textOriginal:
